for i,r in enumerate(self.roots): seqID = str(i) queue = deque([((r,),None, 0, seqID)]) # node, incoming edge and depth amr_triples.append(('root','ROOT',r)) while queue: next,rel,depth,seqID = queue.popleft() for n in next: firsthit = (parent,rel,n) not in self.reentrance_triples leaf = False if self[n] else True
node = Node(rel,n,firsthit,leaf,depth,seqID) #nid += 1 sequence.append(node) if n in visited_nodes or (parent,rel,n) in self.reentrance_triples: continue visited_nodes.add(n) p = len([child for rel,child in self[n].items() if (n,rel,child[0]) not in self.reentrance_triples]) - 1 for rel,child in reversed(self[n].items()): if not (rel,n,child[0]) in amr_triples: if (n,rel,child[0]) not in self.reentrance_triples: queue.append((child,rel,depth+1,seqID+'.'+str(p))) p -= 1 else: queue.append((child,rel,depth+1,None)) amr_triples.append((rel,n,child[0]))
return (sequence,amr_triples)
